    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Hesren Vesh — Junior Clerk Recalled to Hardby</h2>\n<p><em>Junior C&V Hardby clerk who was recalled to Hardby from a Loftwick assignment shortly after the firm became aware of the Yeomanry inquiry. Honest, anxious, and over his head; the party can extract him if they reach him in time.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>Will not fight.</strong> Yields. Has no combat training. If extracted, requires escort.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 0, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 10 · HP 11 (2d8+2) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +0 · Passive Perception 11</p>\n<p>STR 9 · DEX 10 · CON 10 · INT 14 · WIS 13 · CHA 11. Saves: INT +4. Skills: History +3, Insight +3, Investigation +3.</p>\n<p>Languages: Common, Old Aerdi.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 3.</em> See <em>Hardby NPCs → Hesren Vesh — Recalled to Hardby</em> for full profile and extraction logistics.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
